OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FTwo brothers have been jailed for the
OL,7,Fkilling an "entirely innocent" teenage
OL,8,Fboy who was mowed down by a car in
OL,9,FSheffield.
OL,11,F16-year-old Abdullah Yaser Abdullah
OL,12,FTaleb, also known as Abdullah Al
OL,13,FYazidi, was killed when he was hit by
OL,14,Fan Audi driven by Zulkernain Ahmed on
OL,15,FJune 4 last year as he walked along
OL,16,FStaniforth Road.
OL,18,FThe judge at Sheffield Crown Court
OL,19,Fsaid he was "tragically in the wrong
OL,20,Fplace at the wrong time."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FHe had arrived in the UK from war-torn
OL,7,FYemen just two months before he died
OL,8,Fand was due to start college later
OL,9,Fthat year.
OL,11,FAbdullah was seen throwing and
OL,12,Fcatching a water bottle as he walked
OL,13,Falong a pavement moments before he was
OL,14,Fstruck. He was thrown in the air by
OL,15,Fthe impact and died in hospital.
OL,17,FZulkernain Ahmed was out looking for
OL,18,FLa'rome Divers after a dispute about e-
OL,19,Fbikes, and had taken a baseball bat
OL,20,Fwith him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FMr Divers, who was seriously injured,
OL,7,Frefused to make a statement to police.
OL,9,FGraphic footage showed the car driving
OL,10,Fat a group of balaclava-clad riders
OL,11,Fand hitting Mr Divers, before mowing
OL,12,Fdown Abdullah.
OL,14,FAhmed's brother Armaan Ahmed was a
OL,15,Fback seat passenger in the Audi.
OL,17,FThe car U-turned in the road, driving
OL,18,Fback past the scene before abandoning
OL,19,Fthe vehicle.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FThe brothers returned home to collect
OL,7,Fpassports and money before attempting
OL,8,Fto flee the country.
OL,10,FThey were arrested as they tried to
OL,11,Fboard a ferry at the Port of Dover in
OL,12,Fthe early hours of the next day.
OL,14,FSentencing the defendants, Mrs Justice
OL,15,FAmanda Tipples said Abdullah's death
OL,16,Fwas "senseless and shocking."
OL,18,F21-year-old Zulkernain Ahmed was found
OL,19,Fguilty of murdering Abdullah in
OL,20,FFebruary.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FAhmed, of Locke Drive, Darnall, was
OL,7,Falso found guilty of causing e-bike
OL,8,Frider La'rome Divers grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm with intent and attempting to
OL,10,Fcause the other two riders - who have
OL,11,Fnever been identified - grievous
OL,12,Fbodily harm with intent.
OL,14,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,15,Fterm of 30 years for the murder of
OL,16,FAbdullah Yaser Abdullah Taleb.
OL,18,FArmaan Ahmed, 27, of the same address,
OL,19,Fwas cleared of murder but found guilty
OL,20,Fof manslaughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FArmaan Ahmed was also found guilty of
OL,7,Fcausing Mr Divers grievous bodily
OL,8,Fharm. He was jailed for 17 years for
OL,9,Fmanslaughter at Sheffield Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe was also jailed for three years and
OL,12,Fnine months for GBH, which will be
OL,13,Fserved alongside his manslaughter
OL,14,Fsentence.
OL,16,FAnother Ahmed brother, Zain, was the
OL,17,Ffront seat passenger, but has not yet
OL,18,Fbeen traced by police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FAt the beginning of Ahmed's sentencing
OL,7,Fhearing on Thursday, a statement was
OL,8,Fread from Abdullah's father, Yaser
OL,9,FAbdullah Taleb Al Yazidi.
OL,11,FMr Al Yazidi said his son came to the
OL,12,FUK for safety.
OL,14,FHe said in the statement: "Life in
OL,15,FYemen was almost impossible - war,
OL,16,Fgangs, and individuals carrying
OL,17,Fweapons. I travelled to England in
OL,18,Fsearch of safety and for a better life
OL,19,Ffor me and my family."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FMr Al Yazidi said of his son: "He was
OL,7,Fan optimistic person who loved life
OL,8,Fand loved people. He was eager to
OL,9,Flearn and integrate into the community.
OL,11,F"He was happy to arrive in a safe
OL,12,Fcountry. He was very intelligent,
OL,13,Falways smiling, quick to learn and
OL,14,Floved by everyone. He was a pillar of
OL,15,Fthe family."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780683078
OL,3,CBrothers who mowed down and killed
OL,4,C'innocent' teenage boy jailed
OL,6,FMr Al Yazidi said Abdullah was both
OL,7,Fhis son and a friend, adding: "His
OL,8,Fdeath was a devastating blow to all of
OL,9,Fthe family members. This criminal
OL,10,Fincident has destroyed the entire
OL,11,Ffamily."
OL,13,FHe added that Abdullah's mother "is in
OL,14,Fa state of complete collapse" and now
OL,15,Frarely leaves the house.
OL,17,FMr Al Yazidi said Adullah's sisters
OL,18,F"have lost trust in the community and
OL,19,Fare wondering all the time why this
OL,20,Fhas happened".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
